<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[الإِرْذَال]</span>: أرذله: أي جعله رَذْلًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[م]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[إِرذامُ]</span> الإِناء: مَلْؤه.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>و <span class="c4">[الإِرذاء]</span>: أرذيت الناقةَ: أي تركتها رذيةً: أي مهزولة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>والمَرذيّ <span class="c2">«١»</span> والمرذَى: المنبوذ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">يقال:</span> أرذيته: أي نبذته.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
